## 5. Live delivery — основа реактивности UI

### 5.1. Mechanism selection

| Use case | Best fit |
|---|---|
| Bidirectional realtime (chat, collab editor) | **WebSocket** |
| One-way server → client push (notifications, live feed) | **Server-Sent Events (SSE)** |
| Server → external systems | **Webhooks** (HTTP POST) |
| Periodic check (slow data) | **Polling с ETag** (cheap if no change) |

### 5.2. SSE preferred over WebSocket для one-way

Проще: HTTP-based, auto-reconnect, plain text, через any proxy / CDN. Полные HTTP semantics (auth, gzip, headers).

### 5.3. Webhook design

- **Signed payloads** (HMAC) обязательно — receiver verifies authenticity
- **Retry с exponential backoff** при 5xx (документировать policy, например, 3 retries с 1m / 5m / 30m delay)
- **At-least-once delivery** — receiver должен быть idempotent (см. § 2)
- **Event ID** в payload для deduplication
- **Replay endpoint** — `GET /v1/events/<id>` чтобы клиент мог re-fetch при потере

### 5.4. WebSocket connection management

- **Heartbeat** (ping / pong) каждые 30s — detect dead connections
- **Reconnect strategy** с exponential backoff (don't thunder при server restart)
- **Resume protocol** — `last_event_id` для replay missed events после reconnect
- **Backpressure** — server может drop / queue если client slow

