## 14. Frameworks-first для backend

### 14.1. Framework selection

Зависит от language и scale. Популярные modern picks:

| Language | Framework | Когда |
|---|---|---|
| **Go** | Echo / Chi / Fiber / std net/http | Все scales; std net/http для simple |
| **Rust** | Axum / Actix / Rocket | High-performance, type-safe |
| **Python** | FastAPI (async, modern) / Django (full-stack) / Flask (micro) | FastAPI для new API services |
| **Node.js** | Hono / Fastify / NestJS / Express | Hono cross-runtime; Fastify для perf; NestJS для structured |
| **Kotlin** | Ktor (lightweight) / Spring Boot (mature) | Ktor для new; Spring для enterprise integration |
| **Elixir** | Phoenix | High-concurrency / realtime |
| **Ruby** | Rails (full-stack) / Sinatra (micro) | Rails для full-stack web |

### 14.2. Не пишем сами

| Категория | Готовое |
|---|---|
| HTTP framework | см. § 14.1 |
| Validation | `pydantic` / `zod` / `validator.go` / framework-built-in |
| Serialization | framework-built-in |
| Auth (JWT) | `jose` (Go), `pyjwt` (Python), `jsonwebtoken` (Node), framework integrations |
| OAuth | `goth` / `authlib` / `passport.js` / OAuth2 proxy |
| Rate limiting | `tollbooth` / `slowapi` / `express-rate-limit` / API gateway level |
| Caching | Redis client library |
| Message broker | RabbitMQ / NATS / Kafka client libraries |
| Background jobs | Sidekiq / Celery / asynq / inngest |
| OpenAPI spec | framework-generated (FastAPI / Huma / NestJS Swagger / etc) |
| Logging | structured logger native to language |
| Tracing | OpenTelemetry SDK |

