## 15. Backend-specific checklist

В дополнение к `ui-style-guide-base.md` § 7:

- [ ] SLO defined для каждого interactive endpoint (p50 / p99)
- [ ] Долгие операции — 202 Accepted async pattern (не блокировать)
- [ ] Idempotency: PUT / DELETE inherently idempotent; POST creates support `Idempotency-Key` header
- [ ] Errors — RFC 7807 Problem Details (`application/problem+json`)
- [ ] Errors включают machine-code (стабильный) + human title/detail (локализованный)
- [ ] Validation errors per-field (не «form invalid»)
- [ ] Bulk operations для multi-item flows (frontend не loops single-item endpoints)
- [ ] Live delivery механизм выбран осмысленно (WebSocket / SSE / webhook / polling)
- [ ] Webhooks signed + retry с exponential backoff + at-least-once + dedup ID
- [ ] Cursor-based pagination (не offset) + stable sort с tiebreaker
- [ ] Resources modeled по user mental model, не БД схеме
- [ ] URI conventions: plural collections, no verbs в CRUD
- [ ] Versioning стратегия (URI prefix или date header) выбрана и применяется
- [ ] Auth: short access + long refresh, silent refresh в frontend
- [ ] Rate limits с `X-RateLimit-*` headers + 429 + `Retry-After`
- [ ] HTTP cache headers (ETag / Cache-Control) для GET
- [ ] Schema additive по умолчанию; breaking changes → version bump
- [ ] Deprecation / Sunset headers + migration link для phased removal
- [ ] Metrics (rate / latency / error rate) per endpoint
- [ ] Health endpoints (`/healthz` / `/readyz` / `/version`)
- [ ] Structured logs с request_id propagation
- [ ] OpenAPI / AsyncAPI / SDL spec — single source of truth
- [ ] Generated client SDKs для supported languages
- [ ] Sandbox / test mode environment
- [ ] TLS 1.3 + HSTS
- [ ] CORS whitelist explicit
- [ ] Server-side validation обязательна (frontend = UX, не security)
- [ ] Никаких secrets / PII в response без explicit access check
- [ ] Audit log для auth / PII access / admin actions
